call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn

Forbes (SAS) lifts his pivot foot at the start of the dribble.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Mills (SAS) legally deflects the pass and it touches Beal (WAS) last before going out of bounds.
Aldridge (SAS) has a resting hand on Bertans (WAS) that does not affect his ability to defend the shot.
Wagner (WAS) and Aldridge (SAS) briefly engage and disengage.
DeRozan (SAS) takes fewer than three steps after he has gathered the ball.
Forbes (SAS) makes contact to Beal's (WAS) arm and the contact dislodges the ball.
Aldridge (SAS) is firming up and makes marginal contact with McRae (WAS) during the screen.

Wagner (WAS) makes contact to DeRozan's (SAS) arm during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
